These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, azalea
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, country
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, japanese
There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, grey
1. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the japanese##3
2. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4
3. the fan of country is the person who growsaconite##1
4. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Flower      | aconite  | azalea   |
| Music-Genre   | country     | funk   |
| Nationality         | japanese | argentine |
| Color     | light-blue | grey    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  journalist, software-developer
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, bongani
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, yellow
1. the bongani-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking fanta is the person who likes yellow##1
3. the software-developer is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Job          | journalist     | software-developer |
| Beverage   | lemonade | fanta  |
| Cigar           | bongani         | alhambra     |
| Color     | mauve   | yellow    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, cooking
There are 2 different favourite colors: emerald, blood-red
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, blues
City: san-francisco, boston
1. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
2. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Hobby    | cooking     | chess |
| Color         | blood-red | emerald    |
| Music-Genre         | r&b         | blues        |
| City   | san-francisco         | boston    |

