.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, december
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, pakistani
There are 2 different favourite colors: yellow, turquise
2 different pets are kept: dog, ferret
1. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Birthday      | december     | june |
| Nationality          | pakistani   | italian  |
| Color         | yellow | turquise     |
| Pet   | dog  | ferret         |

