.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, dancing
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, daffodil
There 2 different types of food: pepper, tomato
1. the person eating tomato is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking tea is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Beverage           | tea | milk    |
| Hobby   | gardening       | dancing |
| Flower           | sunflower         | daffodil    |
| Food         | pepper    | tomato   |

