The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, december
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Flower      | aconite | marigold       |
| Sport          | badminton   | skateboarding    |
| Transport           | car   | bus |
| Birthday   | december      | november    |

