3. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
4. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| Hobby           | rock-climbing | camping |
| Food   | radish    | kiwi      |
| City           | london      | colone          |
| Cigar         | bolivar | aristoff       |

