.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
City: london, liverpool
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, drama
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, spinach
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, chestnut
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
2. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
3. the person who likes green is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| City    | london | liverpool    |
| Movie-Genre         | drama        | action |
| Food         | raspberry          | spinach     |
| Color   | green        | chestnut     |

 